[{"id":"108a1c289803222faa7ca573ceda467d","from":"Lesley Groff","from_email":"lesley@nysgllc.com","to":"J. Epstein","to_list":[{"name":"J. Epstein","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"FW: Jeffrey","date":"2008-03-14T19:40:24.000Z","formatted_date":"Mar 14, 2008","formatted_time":"7:40 PM","body":" \n \n \n \n \n \n \nLesley Groff\nExecutive Assistant to Jeffrey Epstein\n \n \n\n________________________________\n\nFrom: Simon, Laetitia [mailto:Laetitia.Simon@umusic.com] \nSent: Friday, March 14, 2008 1:29 PM\nTo: Lesley Groff\nSubject: RE: Jeffrey\n\n\n\nHello Lesley,\n\nHave you gotten any news from Jeffrey ??\n\nThanks\n\n \n\n________________________________\n\nDe : Lesley Groff [mailto:lesley@nysgllc.com] \nEnvoy\u00e9 : mardi 11 mars 2008 19:02\n\u00c0 : Simon, Laetitia\nObjet : RE: Jeffrey\n\n \n\nI will pass it along!\n\n \n\nFrom: Simon, Laetitia [mailto:Laetitia.Simon@umusic.com] \nSent: Tuesday, March 11, 2008 2:01 PM\nTo: Lesley Groff\nSubject: Jeffrey\n\n \n\nHello Lesley,\n\nCould you please transfer this email to Jeffry please.\n\nThanks a lot\n\nTake care\n\n \n\nHello Jeffrey,\n\nHow are you? I was expecting you in France last week end but aparently it has been changed. Let me know when you are coming so I try my best to organise your venue!\n\nAlso I have 2 things I need to ask you if of course you can help me out\u2026 I\u2019m trying to take 5 days off in May I need to get away from here :-) from the 30th til the 4th do you think you\u2019ll be able to help me with an apartment? Also regarding my financial situation as we were talking on the phone I\u2019m working 2jobs trying to survive but I\u2019m having a hard time finishing paying my bills do you think you can loan me 1500\u20ac or less, anything you can do will help (even 500\u20ac) and be appreciate\u2026 Thanks let me know\n\nTake Care and say hi to Sarah for me\n\n \n\nLaetitia  Simon \n\nAssistante de direction du label AZ\n\nUniversal Music\n\n20 rue des fosses st jacques\n\n75005 Paris\n\ntel: 01 44 41 50 65\n\nportable: 06 70 45 48 55\n\nfax: 01 44 41 50 60\n\n \n\nLes coulisses du label AZ en un seul clic sur http://rss.universalmusic.fr/podcast/az/ <http://rss.universalmusic.fr/podcast/az/> \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n","body_html":"<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0 Transitional//EN\">\n<HTML xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40\" xmlns:v = \n\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" xmlns:o = \n\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" xmlns:w = \n\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word\" xmlns:st1 = \n\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags\" xmlns:ns0 = \n\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/office/2004/12/omml\"><HEAD>\n<META http-equiv=Content-Type content=\"text/html; charset=windows-1258\">\n<META content=\"MSHTML 6.00.3790.94\" name=GENERATOR><!--[if !mso]>\n<STYLE>v\\:* {\n\tBEHAVIOR: url(#default#VML)\n}\no\\:* {\n\tBEHAVIOR: url(#default#VML)\n}\nw\\:* {\n\tBEHAVIOR: url(#default#VML)\n}\n.shape {\n\tBEHAVIOR: url(#default#VML)\n}\n</STYLE>\n<![endif]--><o:SmartTagType name=\"country-region\" \nnamespaceuri=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags\"></o:SmartTagType><o:SmartTagType \nname=\"place\" \nnamespaceuri=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags\"></o:SmartTagType><!--[if !mso]>\n<STYLE>st1\\:* {\n\tBEHAVIOR: url(#default#ieooui)\n}\n</STYLE>\n<![endif]-->\n<STYLE>@font-face {\n\tfont-family: Wingdings;\n}\n@font-face {\n\tfont-family: Tahoma;\n}\n@font-face {\n\tfont-family: Georgia;\n}\n@font-face {\n\tfont-family: Calibri;\n}\n@page Section1 {size: 595.3pt 841.9pt; margin: 70.85pt 70.85pt 70.85pt 70.85pt; }\nA:link {\n\tmso-style-priority: 99\n}\nSPAN.MSOHYPERLINK {\n\tmso-style-priority: 99\n}\nA:visited {\n\tmso-style-priority: 99\n}\nSPAN.MSOHYPERLINKFOLLOWED {\n\tmso-style-priority: 99\n}\nP.MsoNormal {\n\tFONT-SIZE: 12pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"Times New Roman\"\n}\nLI.MsoNormal {\n\tFONT-SIZE: 12pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"Times New Roman\"\n}\nDIV.MsoNormal {\n\tFO