ADDING-LEFT: 0cm; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-TOP: 3pt; BORDER-BOTTOM: medium none\">\n<P class=MsoNormal><B><FONT face=Tahoma size=2><SPAN lang=EN-US \nstyle=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma\">From:</SPAN></FONT></B><FONT \nface=Tahoma size=2><SPAN lang=EN-US \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma\"> Simon, Laetitia \n[mailto:Laetitia.Simon@umusic.com] <BR><B><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold\">Sent:</SPAN></B> Tuesday, March 11, 2008 2:01 \nPM<BR><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold\">To:</SPAN></B> Lesley Groff<BR><B><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold\">Subject:</SPAN></B> \nJeffrey<o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P></DIV></DIV>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\" size=3><SPAN lang=EN-US \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=Arial size=2><SPAN lang=EN-GB \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">Hello \nLesley,<o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=Arial size=2><SPAN lang=EN-GB \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">Could you please transfer this email \nto Jeffry please.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=Arial size=2><SPAN lang=EN-GB \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">Thanks a \nlot<o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=Arial size=2><SPAN lang=EN-GB \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">Take \ncare<o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=Arial size=2><SPAN lang=EN-GB \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=Arial size=2><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">Hello \nJeffrey,<o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=Arial size=2><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">How are you? </SPAN></FONT><FONT \nface=Arial size=2><SPAN lang=EN-GB style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">I \nwas expecting you in <st1:country-region w:st=\"on\"><st1:place \nw:st=\"on\">France</st1:place></st1:country-region> last week end but aparently it \nhas been changed. Let me know when you are coming so I try my best to organise \nyour venue!<o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=Arial size=2><SPAN lang=EN-GB \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">Also I have 2 things I need to ask \nyou if of course you can help me out\u2026 I\u2019m trying to take 5 days off in May I \nneed to get away from here </SPAN></FONT><FONT face=Wingdings size=2><SPAN \nlang=EN-GB style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Wingdings\">J</SPAN></FONT><FONT \nface=Arial size=2><SPAN lang=EN-GB style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"> \nfrom the 30<SUP>th</SUP> til the 4<SUP>th</SUP> do you think you\u2019ll be able to \nhelp me with an apartment? Also regarding my financial situation as we were \ntalking on the phone I\u2019m working 2jobs trying to survive but I\u2019m having a hard \ntime finishing paying my bills do you think you can loan me 1500\u20ac or less, \nanything you can do will help (even 500\u20ac) and be appreciate\u2026 Thanks let me \nknow<o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=Arial size=2><SPAN lang=EN-GB \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">Take Care and say hi to Sarah for \nme<o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=Arial size=2><SPAN lang=EN-GB \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><EM><I><FONT face=Georgia size=2><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia\">Laetitia&nbsp; Simon \n</SPAN></FONT></I></EM><o:p></o:p></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><EM><I><FONT face=Georgia size=2><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia\">Assistante de direction du label \nAZ</SPAN></FONT></I></EM><o:p></o:p></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><EM><I><FONT face=Georgia size=2><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia\">Universal \nMusic</SPAN></FONT></I></EM><o:p></o:p></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><EM><I><FONT face=Georgia size=2><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia\">20 rue des fosses st \njacques</SPAN></FONT></I></EM><o:p></o:p></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><EM><I><FONT face=Georgia size=2><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia\">75005 \nParis</SPAN></FONT></I></EM><o:p></o:p></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><EM><I><FONT face=Georgia size=2><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia\">tel: 01 44 41 50 \n65</SPAN></FONT></I></EM><o:p></o:p></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><EM><I><FONT face=Georgia size=2><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia\">portable: 06 70 45 48 \n55</SPAN></FONT></I></EM><o:p></o:p></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><EM><I><FONT face=Georgia size=2><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia\">fax: 01 44 41 50 \n60</SPAN></FONT></I></EM><o:p></o:p></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\" size=3><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><EM><I><FONT face=Georgia size=2><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia\">Les coulisses du label AZ en un \nseul clic sur </SPAN></FONT></I></EM><A \nhref=\"http://rss.universalmusic.fr/podcast/az/\"><EM><I><FONT face=Georgia \ncolor=black size=2><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia; TEXT-DECORATION: none\">http://rss.universalmusic.fr/podcast/az/</SPAN></FONT></I></EM></A><o:p></o:p></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\" size=3><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\" size=3><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\" size=3><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></FONT></P></DIV></BODY></HTML>\n","is_from_epstein":false,"attachments":0,"avatar_color":"#0f9d58","stars":22,"is_redacted":false},{"id":"a57ba849cba409bdb04be50cae01f35c","from":"Lesley Groff","from_email":"lesley@nysgllc.com","to":"J. Epstein","to_list":[{"name":"J. Epstein","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"FW: Jeffrey","date":"2008-03-11T18:01:53.000Z","formatted_date":"Mar 11, 2008","formatted_time":"6:01 PM","body":" \n\n \n\nFrom: Simon, Laetitia [mailto:Laetitia.Simon@umusic.com] \nSent: Tuesday, March 11, 2008 2:01 PM\nTo: Lesley Groff\nSubject: Jeffrey\n\n \n\nHello Lesley,\n\nCould you please transfer this email to Jeffry please.\n\nThanks a lot\n\nTake care\n\n \n\nHello Jeffrey,\n\nHow are you? I was expecting you in France last week end but aparently it has been changed. Let me know when you are coming so I try my best to organise your venue!\n\nAlso I have 2 things I need to ask you if of course you can help me out\u2026 I\u2019m trying to take 5 days off in May I need to get away from here J from the 30th til the 4th do you think you\u2019ll be able to help me with an apartment? Also regarding my financial situation as we were talking on the phone I\u2019m working 2jobs trying to survive but I\u2019m having a hard time finishing paying my bills do you think you can loan me 1500\u20ac or less, anything you can do will help (even 500\u20ac) and be appreciate\u2026 Thanks let me know\n\nTake Care and say hi to Sarah for me\n\n \n\nLaetitia  Simon \n\nAssistante de direction du label AZ\n\nUniversal Music\n\n20 rue des fosses st jacques\n\n75005 Paris\n\ntel: 01 44 41 50 65\n\nportable: 06 70 45 48 55\n\nfax: 01 44 41 50 60\n\n \n\nLes coulisses du label AZ en un seul clic sur http://rss.universalmusic.fr/podcast/az/ <http://rss.universalmusic.fr/podcast/az/> \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n","body_html":"<html xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" xmlns:w=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word\" xmlns:m=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/office/2004/12/omml\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40\">\n\n<head>\n<meta http-equiv=Content-Type content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\">\n<meta name=Generator content=\"Microsoft Word 12 (filtered medium)\">\n<style>\n<!--\n /* Font Definitions */\n @font-face\n\t{font-family:Wingdings;\n\tpanose-1:5 0 0 0 0 0 0 0 0 0;}\n@font-face\n\t{font-family:Wingdings;\n\tpanose-1:5 0 0 0 0 0 0 0 0 0;}\n@font-face\n\t{font-family:Calibri;\n\tpanose-1:2 15 5 2 2 2 4 3 2 4;}\n@font-face\n\t{font-family:Tahoma;\n\tpanose-1:2 11 6 4 3 5 4 4 2 4;}\n@font-face\n\t{font-family:Georgia;\n\tpanose-1:2 4 5 2 5 4 5 2 3 3;}\n /* Style Definitions */\n p.MsoNormal, li.MsoNormal, div.MsoNormal\n\t{margin:0in;\n\tmargin-bottom:.0001pt;\n\tfont-size:12.0pt;\n\tfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\";}\na:link, span.MsoHyperlink\n\t{mso-style-priority:99;\n\tcolor:blue;\n\ttext-decoration:underline;}\na:visited, span.MsoHyperlinkFollowed\n\t{mso-style-priority:99;\n\tcolor:purple;\n\ttext-decoration:underline;}\nspan.EmailStyle17\n\t{mso-style-type:personal;\n\tfont-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\n\tcolor:windowtext;}\nspan.EmailStyle19\n\t{mso-style-type:personal-reply;\n\tfont-family:\"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\";\n\tcolor:#1F497D;}\n.MsoChpDefault\n\t{mso-style-type:export-only;\n\tfont-size:10.0pt;}\n@page Section1\n\t{size:595.3pt 841.9pt;\n\tmargin:70.85pt 70.85pt 70.85pt 70.85pt;}\ndiv.Section1\n\t{page:Section1;}\n-->\n</style>\n<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\n <o:shapedefaults v:ext=\"edit\" spidmax=\"1026\" />\n</xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\n <o:shapelayout v:ext=\"edit\">\n  <o:idmap v:ext=\"edit\" data=\"1\" />\n </o:shapelayout></xml><![endif]-->\n</head>\n\n<body lang=EN-US link=blue vlink=purple>\n\n<div class=Section1>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:#1F497D'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:#1F497D'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\n\n<div>\n\n<div style='border:none;border-top:solid #B5C4DF 1.0pt;padding:3.0pt 0in 0in 0in'>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><b><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Tahoma\",\"sans-serif\"'>From:</span></b><span\nstyle='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Tahoma\",\"sans-serif\"'> Simon, Laetitia\n[mailto:Laetitia.Simon@umusic.com] <br>\n<b>Sent:</b> Tuesday, March 11, 2008 2:01 PM<br>\n<b>To:</b> Lesley Groff<br>\n<b>Subject:</b> Jeffrey<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-GB style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\"'>Hello\nLesley,<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-GB style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\"'>Could\nyou please transfer this email to Jeffry please.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-GB style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\"'>Thanks\na lot<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-GB style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\"'>Take\ncare<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-GB style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\"'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=FR style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\"'>Hello\nJeffrey,<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=FR style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\"'>How\nare you? </span><span lang=EN-GB style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\"'>I\nwas expecting you in France last week end but aparently it has been changed.\nLet me know when you are coming so I try my best to organise your venue!<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-GB style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\"'>Also\nI have 2 things I need to ask you if of course you can help me out\u2026 I\u2019m trying\nto take 5 days off in May I need to get away from here </span><span lang=EN-GB\nstyle='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Wingdings'>J</span><span lang=EN-GB\nstyle='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\"'> from the 30<sup>th</sup>\ntil the 4<sup>th</sup> do you think you\u2019ll be able to help me with an\napartment? Also regarding my financial situation as we were talking on the\nphone I\u2019m working 2jobs trying to survive but I\u2019m having a hard time finishing\npaying my bills do you think you can loan me 1500\u20ac or less, anything you can do\nwill help (even 500\u20ac) and be appreciate\u2026 Thanks let me know<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-GB style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\"'>Take\nCare and say hi to Sarah for me<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-GB style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\"'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><em><span lang=FR style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Georgia\",\"serif\"'>Laetitia&nbsp;\nSimon </span></em><span lang=FR><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><em><span lang=FR style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Georgia\",\"serif\"'>Assistante\nde direction du label AZ</span></em><span lang=FR><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><em><span lang=FR style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Georgia\",\"serif\"'>Universal\nMusic</span></em><span lang=FR><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><em><span lang=FR style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Georgia\",\"serif\"'>20\nrue des fosses st jacques</span></em><span lang=FR><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><em><span lang=FR style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Georgia\",\"serif\"'>75005\nParis</span></em><span lang=FR><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><em><span lang=FR style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Georgia\",\"serif\"'>tel:\n01 44 41 50 65</span></em><span lang=FR><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><em><span lang=FR style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Georgia\",\"serif\"'>portable:\n06 70 45 48 55</span></em><span lang=FR><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><em><span lang=FR style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Georgia\",\"serif\"'>fax:\n01 44 41 50 60</span></em><span lang=FR><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=FR>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><em><span lang=FR style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Georgia\",\"serif\"'>Les\ncoulisses du label AZ en un seul clic sur </span></em><span lang=FR><a\nhref=\"http://rss.universalmusic.fr/podcast/az/\"><em><span style='font-size:\n10.0pt;font-family:\"Georgia\",\"serif\";color:windowtext;text-decoration:none'>http://rss.universalmusic.fr/podcast/az/</span></em></a><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=FR>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=FR>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=FR><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n</body>\n\n</html>\n","is_from_epstein":false,"attachments":0,"avatar_color":"#0f9d58","stars":1,"is_redacted":false}]